snippet: France's centre-right UDI party is set to withdraw its support on Friday for presidential candidate Francois Fillon, a source close to the party's leadership told Reuters as the scandal-hit conservative loses backers....
lead_paragraph: France's centre-right UDI party is set to withdraw its support on Friday for presidential candidate Francois Fillon, a source close to the party's leadership told Reuters as the scandal-hit conservative loses backers.
